{"id": "1421416203011887194", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "91273658663698432", "author_name": "wolfmaw", "content": "If you want \"reliable\", an Aequor/Caro comp is pretty sturdy. Have innate healing on-demand with Caro, and tons of utility from tentacles.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T08:40:31.434000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-27T08:41:11.200000+00:00"}
{"id": "1421417352385269790", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "91273658663698432", "author_name": "wolfmaw", "content": "As for individual units: Sanga has decent tentacle generation, and Agrippa can stack up poison really well as well as generate a decent amount of shields.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T08:45:05.466000+00:00"}
